Package org.jivesoftware.smackx.workgroup

Interface Summary
WorkgroupInvitationListener An interface which all classes interested in hearing about group chat invitations should implement.
 

Class Summary
MetaData MetaData packet extension.
QueueUser An immutable class which wraps up customer-in-queue data return from the server; depending on the type of information dispatched from the server, not all information will be available in any given instance.
WorkgroupInvitation An immutable class wrapping up the basic information which comprises a group chat invitation.
